author: Matt Walsh
description:
Today on the Matt Walsh Show, Pope Leo hosts a “climate justice” event at the Vatican. Should climate justice be a priority in the midst of Christian persecution all over the globe? Should it be the priority under any circumstance at all? Also, the Trump Administration restores law and order to Memphis. Don Lemon lashes out against white men, again. And Secretary of War Pete Hegseth launches a horrific and bigoted attack against the bearded community.
